quotas.name: Pondicherry Govt Quota
quotas.tooltip_content: **Eligibility for the Quota : Pondicherry Govt Quota** Residents of the U.T. of Puducherry 1. Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application **(or)** 2. Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence) 3. Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed 4. Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school. Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state 5. Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action **and** children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T 6. French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced ---

Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence) 3. Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed 4. Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school. Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state 5. Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action **and** children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T 6. French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced ---

  1. Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application (or)



  2. Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence)



  3. Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed



  4. Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school.
    Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state



  5. Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T



  6. French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced

quota.tooltip_content: **Eligibility for the Quota : Pondicherry Govt Quota - Yanam** **Residents of the U.T. of Puducherry - Yanam** 1) Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application **(or)** 2) Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence) 3) Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed 4) Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school. Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state 5) Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T 6) French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced ---

Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed 4) Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school. Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state 5) Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T 6) French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced ---

Residents of the U.T. of Puducherry - Yanam


1) Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application (or)


2) Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence)


3) Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed


4) Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school.
Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state


5) Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T


6) French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced

  1. Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application (or)



  2. Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence)



  3. Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed



  4. Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school.
    Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state



  5. Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T



  6. French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced

Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed 4) Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school. Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state 5) Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T 6) French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced ---
quota.tooltip_content_html:
Eligibility for the Quota : Pondicherry Govt Quota - Karaikal


Residents of the U.T. of Puducherry - Karaikal


1) Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application (or)


2) Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence)


3) Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed


4) Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school.
Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state


5) Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T


6) French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced

Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence) 3. Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed 4. Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The chidlren in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school. Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state 5. Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action **and** children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T 6. French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced ---

Residents of the U.T. of Puducherry** 1) Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application **(or)** 2) Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence) 3) Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed 4) Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The children in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school. Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state 5) Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T 6) French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced ---

Pondicherry Govt School candidates. Residents of the U.T. of Puducherry


1) Candidate / One of the Parents /Guardian (if parents are not alive) has been residing continuously in Pondicherry UT for at least 5 years preceding the date of application (or)


2) Passed SSLC/HSC or any other public exam and studied continuously for 5 classes immediately preceding the HSC (including the year of HSC ) in in Pondicherry UT and having their residence in Pondicherry UT for 5 years continuously during that period.(Hostels not considered residence)


3) Children of natives of U.T. of Puducherry who have declared any place in U.T. of Puducherry as their home town and so certified by their respective Heads of Office. Nativity Certificate in the prescribed format has to be enclosed


4) Children of Central/ State Government Servants/ Defense Personnel/ Central Paramilitary Forces/ Employees of Public Sector Undertakings wholly or substantially owned either by the Central Govt or Puducherry Administration serving in U.T. of Puducherry continuously for last 3 years prior to the application submission. The children in this case should have complete XI and XII in Puducherry school, should have passed XII in same school.
Those claiming residence in Puducherry cannot claim residence in any other state


5) Children of Defence Personnel who were killed or disabled in action and children of Central Government Servants/ Pondicherry U.T. Government Servants/Defence Personnel/ Employees of Public Sector Undertaking who died while in the service in the Puducherry U.T


6) French nationals residing in the Puducherry U.T. as per “Treaty of Cession” who produce the prescribed Puducherry U.T. Residence Certificate. “Certificate of Registration” by French Consulate to be produced
